{"tid":239449,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"口才好既定義","createTime":"2017-05-11T16:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T16:38:38.000Z","uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cee7ff82a8be51d2b428d02a71609af2c68b6028","tid":239449,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"上網見到好多人對口才好既定義都唔同 好似岩岩我見到既呢段野：<br />\n究竟什麼是口才？通俗理解，口才就是說話的能力，可這樣定義，不足以讓人對口才有深刻理解，更不足以讓我們找到口才不好的根源和提升方法。所謂說話能力其衡量標準是什麼？<span style=\"color: red;\">聲音洪亮？語音語調好？情感豐富？內容豐富？<br />\n</span><br />\n巴絲們又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如講下你地對口才好既定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c96f6086ee42521ee0cc7e4042370d2eccaf68","tid":239449,"uid":74172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:33:20.000Z","msg":"考到AO"},{"pid":"dd8720dd3636cd3b68eb7fb04dbc3fd87a6ffc0b","tid":239449,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考到AO</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5a9ea8ce88cd4f0c9667b777ada70de40da99e","tid":239449,"uid":99989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"講到好似達哥咁咪叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}